window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The safest place for an outlaw to be is in the arms of the sheriff. </b></p> <p>Grace grew up in a family of outlaws, wild and reckless. The sheriff is intent on justice, but one look at the gun-toting, pants-wearing woman and he knows she’ll belong to him. To Charlie too, for the men at Bridgewater claim - and tame - their bride together.&nbsp;</p> <p>But can they? Do they really know the woman they’ve wed?&nbsp;</p> <p>While they might strip her bare, she’s still hiding plenty of secrets...secrets that might kill them all.</p>"; 
